Package com.weirddev.testme.intellij.template.context

Interface TestMeTemplateParams

public interface TestMeTemplateParams
Custom params injected into Velocity context for test generation templates. Can be accessed from Velocity test templates with the $ operator. i.e. $TESTED_CLASS.canonicalName. Date: 24/10/2016.
Author:
Yaron Yamin
